title: North Yorkshire road closed after flooding
text:
The A165 Ramshill Road has been closed in both directions between West Street and Albion Road due to flooding through burst water main.
The closure affects traffic travelling between Scarborough and Osgodby.
Utility company have advised the road is likely to be closed into the early hours of the morning.
Last updated Wed 14 Oct 2015 Travel Scarborough South Yorkshire Osgodby
